          <strong> Description:</strong><br>
          Automatically suggest study sessions for tasks that do not yet have one.<br><br>
          It creates a StudySession object for each task without a session, and returns a list of scheduled confirmations<br><br>
        <ul>
           <li>default_duration: The length of the session in hours (default is 2).</li> 
            <li>start_date: Optional start date for the sessions; if not provided, today’s date is used.</li>
            <li>Returns: List of strings confirming each session scheduled.</li><br>
            <strong>Purpose:</strong> Helps students quickly generate study sessions for all incomplete tasks, improving task planning and time management
        </ul>
          
        </p>
